com.github.katjahahn.parser.optheader

Enum Subsystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Subsystem>
      • com.github.katjahahn.parser.optheader.Subsystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Characteristic, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Subsystem>

    public enum Subsystem
extends java.lang.Enum<Subsystem>
implements Characteristic
    Represents the subsystem that is required to run this image.

    Descriptions are from the PECOFF specification.
